metadata.name: The Dream Paradise
metadata.description:
This photo is one of my Incredible photo that I've taken. Yes, the EL Nido Island in Philippines is amazing but the best part of this picture is the clouds naturally formed like the PHILIPPINE MAP.  I went up to the cliff to photograph the overlooking paradise, then suddenly I noticed that the clouds in front of me naturally formed like the Philippine Map. This is one of a kind experience you can't miss!

EL Nido, Itâ€™s known for the white sand beaches, coral reefs and as the gateway to the Bacuit archipelago, a group of islands with steep karst cliffs. One of EL Nido Island called Matinloc Shrine, This is a spiritual oasis that houses the Shrine of Our Lady of Matinloc and provides a beautiful view of the jagged cliffs overlooking a crescent-shaped cove.
